[
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhang_shi_wu",
    "speaker_name": "张十五",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这首七言诗，说的是兵火过后，原来的家家户户，都变成了断墙残瓦的破败之地。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 6,
    "line_end": 12
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_xiao_tian",
    "speaker_name": "郭啸天",
    "listener": "char_zhang_shi_wu",
    "text": "张先生，你可是从北方来吗？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 32,
    "line_end": 32
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhang_shi_wu",
    "speaker_name": "张十五",
    "listener": "char_guo_xiao_tian",
    "text": "我中国百姓，比女真人多上一百倍也还不止。只要朝廷肯用忠臣良将，咱们一百个打他一个，金兵如何能够抵挡？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 44,
    "line_end": 44
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_xiao_tian",
    "speaker_name": "郭啸天",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "正是！",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 46,
    "line_end": 46
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhang_shi_wu",
    "speaker_name": "张十五",
    "listener": "char_guo_xiao_tian",
    "text": "岳爷爷有两句诗道：'壮志饥餐胡虏肉，笑谈渴饮匈奴血。'这两句诗当真说出了中国全国百姓的心里话。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 52,
    "line_end": 52
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qu_ling_feng",
    "speaker_name": "曲三",
    "listener": "char_yang_tie_xin",
    "text": "骂得好，骂得对，有什么不对？不过我曾听得人说，想要杀岳爷爷议和的，罪魁祸首却不是秦桧。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 56,
    "line_end": 56
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qu_ling_feng",
    "speaker_name": "曲三",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "秦桧做的是宰相，议和也好，不议和也好，他都做他的宰相。可是岳爷爷一心一意要灭了金国，迎接徽钦二帝回来。这两个皇帝一回来，高宗皇帝他又做什么呀？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 56,
    "line_end": 56
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_xiao_tian",
    "speaker_name": "郭啸天",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "不要脸，不要脸！这鸟皇帝算是那一门子的皇帝！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 66,
    "line_end": 66
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qu_ling_feng",
    "speaker_name": "曲三",
    "listener": "char_guo_xiao_tian",
    "text": "郭兄，就算你有双戟在手，你们两位合力，斗得过我吗？",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 100,
    "line_end": 100
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_xiao_tian",
    "speaker_name": "郭啸天",
    "listener": "char_qu_ling_feng",
    "text": "斗不过！我兄弟俩有眼无珠，跟你老兄在牛家村同住了一年有余，全没瞧出你老兄是位身怀绝技的高手。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 100,
    "line_end": 100
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qu_ling_feng",
    "speaker_name": "曲三",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "资质寻常的，当然是这样，可是天下尽有聪明绝顶之人，文才武功，琴棋书画，算数韬略，以至医卜星相，奇门五行，无一不会，无一不精！只不过你们见不着罢了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 124,
    "line_end": 124
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": "char_yang_tie_xin",
    "text": "叫我留步，是何居心？爽爽快快说出来罢！",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 148,
    "line_end": 148
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "好好好，喝酒就喝酒！",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 152,
    "line_end": 152
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "无耻鼠辈，道爷今日大开杀戒了！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 170,
    "line_end": 170
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yang_tie_xin",
    "speaker_name": "杨铁心",
    "listener": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "text": "来来来，教你知道杨家枪法的厉害。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 172,
    "line_end": 172
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": "char_yang_tie_xin",
    "text": "凭你这公门鼠辈，也配使杨家枪！",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 174,
    "line_end": 174
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "贫道姓丘名处机⋯⋯",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 196,
    "line_end": 196
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_xiao_tian",
    "speaker_name": "郭啸天",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "遮莫不是长春子么？",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 196,
    "line_end": 196
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "出家人本来不可滥杀，可是一见了害民奸贼、敌国仇寇，贫道便不能手下留情。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 230,
    "line_end": 230
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这对短剑是我无意之中得来的，虽然锋锐，但剑刃短了，贫道不合使，将来孩子们倒可用来杀敌防身。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 246,
    "line_end": 246
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yang_tie_xin",
    "speaker_name": "杨铁心",
    "listener": "char_guo_xiao_tian",
    "text": "要是咱们的孩子都是男儿，那么让他们结为兄弟，倘若都是女儿，就结为姊妹⋯⋯",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 250,
    "line_end": 250
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_xiao_tian",
    "speaker_name": "郭啸天",
    "listener": "char_yang_tie_xin",
    "text": "若是一男一女，那就结为夫妻。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 250,
    "line_end": 250
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_han_xiao_ying",
    "speaker_name": "韩小莹",
    "listener": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "text": "丘道长能干英明，天下皆知，我们七兄弟也不是初走江湖之人，这次大家竟胡里胡涂的栽在这无名之辈手里，流传出去，定教江湖上好汉耻笑。这事如何善后，还得请道长示下。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 888,
    "line_end": 888
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
    "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
    "listener": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "text": "丘道长仗剑横行天下，怎把别人瞧在眼里？这事又何必再问我们兄弟？",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 892,
    "line_end": 892
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": "char_ke_zhen_e",
    "text": "贫道无状，行事胡涂，得罪了各位，确是贫道的不是，这里向各位谢过，尚请原宥！",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 894,
    "line_end": 894
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
    "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
    "listener": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "text": "江湖上的事，我兄弟再也没面目理会啦。我们在这里打鱼的打鱼，砍柴的砍柴，只要道长放我们一马，不再前来寻事，我们总可安安稳稳的过这下半辈子。",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 896,
    "line_end": 896
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
    "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
    "listener": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "text": "你把我们兄弟个个打得重伤，单凭这么一句话，就算了事么？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 900,
    "line_end": 900
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
    "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
    "listener": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "text": "这口气我们咽不下去，还求道长再予赐教。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 902,
    "line_end": 902
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "各位既要与贫道再决胜负，也无不可，但办法却要由贫道规定。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 910,
    "line_end": 910
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_han_bao_jv",
    "speaker_name": "韩宝驹",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "怎样？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 934,
    "line_end": 934
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "过得一十八年，孩子们都十八岁了，咱们再在嘉兴府醉仙楼头相会，大邀江湖上的英雄好汉，欢宴一场。酒醉饭饱之余，让两个孩子比试武艺，瞧是贫道的徒弟高明呢，还是七侠的徒弟了得？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 934,
    "line_end": 934
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
    "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "好，咱们赌了。",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 938,
    "line_end": 938
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "古来大英雄真侠士，跟人结交是为朋友卖命，所谓'不爱其躯，赴士之厄困'，只要是义所当为，就是把性命交给了他，又算得什么？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 948,
    "line_end": 948
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_cong",
    "speaker_name": "朱聪",
    "listener": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "text": "道长指点得不错，兄弟知罪了。我们七怪担当这件事就是。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 948,
    "line_end": 948
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "今日是三月廿四，十八年后的今日正午，大伙儿在醉仙楼相会，让普天下英雄见见，谁是真正的好汉子！",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 950,
    "line_end": 950
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tie_mu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "铁木真",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "敌兵还没有疲！",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1028,
    "line_end": 1028
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tie_mu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "铁木真",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "好箭法！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1034,
    "line_end": 1034
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tie_mu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "铁木真",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "好兄弟，真有你的！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1038,
    "line_end": 1038
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "忽都虎",
    "listener": "char_tie_mu_zhen",
    "text": "可以举纛吹号了么？",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1040,
    "line_end": 1040
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tie_mu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "铁木真",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "敌军还没疲，再支持一会。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1040,
    "line_end": 1040
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "哲别",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "水，水⋯⋯给我水？",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1062,
    "line_end": 1062
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "哲别",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "好兄弟，多谢你！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1068,
    "line_end": 1068
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "妈妈说的，应当接待客人，不可要客人东西。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1068,
    "line_end": 1068
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "哲别",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "要是我在战场之上，给胜过我的好汉杀了，那是死得心甘情愿。现今却是大鹰落在地下，为蚂蚁咬死！",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1112,
    "line_end": 1112
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tie_mu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "铁木真",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你还不投降吗？",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1168,
    "line_end": 1168
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "哲别",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "大汗饶我一命，以后赴汤蹈火，我也愿意。横断黑水，粉碎岩石，扶保大汗。征讨外敌，挖取人心！叫我到那里，我就到那里。为大汗冲锋陷阵，奔驰万里，日夜不停！",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1170,
    "line_end": 1170
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tie_mu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "铁木真",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "好好，以后你跟着我罢！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1168,
    "line_end": 1168
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tie_mu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "铁木真",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "好孩儿！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1174,
    "line_end": 1174
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tuo_lei",
    "speaker_name": "拖雷",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "哈，你躲在这里。你不敢去帮拖雷打架，没用的东西！",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1708,
    "line_end": 1708
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_han_xiao_ying",
    "speaker_name": "韩小莹",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "你若赶去，连你也一起吃了，你难道不怕豹子？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1714,
    "line_end": 1714
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_han_xiao_ying",
    "text": "我怕豹子。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1716,
    "line_end": 1716
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_han_xiao_ying",
    "speaker_name": "韩小莹",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "那你去不去？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1714,
    "line_end": 1714
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我去！",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1716,
    "line_end": 1716
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_cong",
    "speaker_name": "朱聪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "孩子虽笨，却正是我辈中人。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1718,
    "line_end": 1718
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_nan_xi_ren",
    "speaker_name": "南希仁",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "回江南，不好！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1768,
    "line_end": 1768
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_nan_xi_ren",
    "speaker_name": "南希仁",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "练武，这里好，江南太舒服，不好！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1770,
    "line_end": 1770
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
    "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "不够！靖儿不聪明。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1768,
    "line_end": 1768
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hua_zheng",
    "speaker_name": "华筝",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "郭靖，又给师父打了么？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1796,
    "line_end": 1796
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hua_zheng",
    "speaker_name": "华筝",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "什么拆招？是挨揍！",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1800,
    "line_end": 1800
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hua_zheng",
    "speaker_name": "华筝",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "我如不嫁给都史，那么嫁给谁？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1926,
    "line_end": 1926
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_hua_zheng",
    "text": "我不知道。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1926,
    "line_end": 1926
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hua_zheng",
    "speaker_name": "华筝",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "你什么都不知道！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1926,
    "line_end": 1926
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tie_mu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "铁木真",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "好孩子，你的箭法好得很啊！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1906,
    "line_end": 1906
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_tie_mu_zhen",
    "text": "是哲别师父教我的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1906,
    "line_end": 1906
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tie_mu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "铁木真",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "师父是哲别，徒弟也是哲别。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1906,
    "line_end": 1906
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_tie_mu_zhen",
    "text": "王罕的孙子都史又恶又坏，华筝嫁给他将来定要吃苦。求求大汗别把华筝许配给他。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 1914,
    "line_end": 1914
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "这种穷地方小酒店，好东西谅来也弄不出来，就这样吧，干果四样是荔枝、桂圆、蒸枣、银杏。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2588,
    "line_end": 2588
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你们这江瑶柱是五年前的宿货，这也能卖钱？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2600,
    "line_end": 2600
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "兄弟，你我一见如故，请把这件衣服穿了去。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2612,
    "line_end": 2612
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "还没请教兄长高姓大名。",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2614,
    "line_end": 2614
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "我姓郭名靖。兄弟你呢？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2614,
    "line_end": 2614
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "我姓黄，单名一个蓉字。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2614,
    "line_end": 2614
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "大哥，我肚子又饿啦。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2614,
    "line_end": 2614
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "爹爹不要我啦。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2620,
    "line_end": 2620
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "不会的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2620,
    "line_end": 2620
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "那么他干么不来找我？",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2620,
    "line_end": 2620
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "或许他是找的，不过没找着。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2620,
    "line_end": 2620
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "大哥，我向你讨一件宝物，你肯么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2622,
    "line_end": 2622
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "那有不肯之理？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2622,
    "line_end": 2622
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "我就是喜欢你这匹汗血宝马。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2622,
    "line_end": 2622
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "好，我送给兄弟便了。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 2622,
    "line_end": 2622
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "speaker_name": "周伯通",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "你是全真七子中那一人门下？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 6197,
    "line_end": 6197
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "text": "弟子郭靖参见前辈，弟子的受业恩师是江南七侠。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 6199,
    "line_end": 6199
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "speaker_name": "周伯通",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "你会降龙十八掌？这套功夫可了不起哪。你传给我好不好？我拜你为师。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 6203,
    "line_end": 6203
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "speaker_name": "周伯通",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "小朋友，你我结义为兄弟如何？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 6219,
    "line_end": 6219
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "text": "弟子是马道长、丘道长的晚辈，该当尊您为师祖爷才是。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 6221,
    "line_end": 6221
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "speaker_name": "周伯通",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我的武艺全是师兄所传，年纪又不比他们大多少，马钰、丘处机他们见我没点长辈样子，也不大敬我是长辈。你多半不是我儿子，我恐怕也不是你儿子，又分什么长辈晚辈？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 6223,
    "line_end": 6223
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "speaker_name": "周伯通",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你不肯和我结拜，定是嫌我太老，其实我胡子虽长，年纪并不老，呜呜呜⋯⋯我把胡子拔得光光的，那就不老了！",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 6231,
    "line_end": 6231
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "speaker_name": "周伯通",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "老顽童周伯通，今日与郭靖义结金兰，日后有福共享，有难共当。如若违此盟誓，教我武功全失，连小狗小猫也打不过。",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 6237,
    "line_end": 6237
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "郭靖今日与老顽童周伯通义结金兰⋯⋯连小老鼠小乌龟也打不过。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 6239,
    "line_end": 6239
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "speaker_name": "周伯通",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "黄老邪小气得紧，给人这般淡酒喝。只有那天一个美丽小姑娘送来的美酒，喝起来才有点酒味，可惜从此她又不来了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 6241,
    "line_end": 6241
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "text": "我我⋯⋯我蠢得很，功夫老学不会，惹得六位恩师生气。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 6196,
    "line_end": 6196
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "speaker_name": "周伯通",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "你待怎样？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 6196,
    "line_end": 6196
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "text": "我日夜拚命苦练，可总不行，说什么也不行⋯⋯",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 6196,
    "line_end": 6196
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "你练得就算骆驼一般，壮是壮了，但骆驼打得赢豹子吗？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 1776,
    "line_end": 1776
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "可惜你不爱做叫化，否则似你这般人品，我帮中倒还没人及得上，我这根打狗棒非传给你不可。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 7367,
    "line_end": 7367
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "text": "老毒物，你千方百计要占我上风，老天爷总是不许！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 7355,
    "line_end": 7355
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "老叫化最爱的就是吃喝，老毒物偏生瞄准了来折磨人。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 7403,
    "line_end": 7403
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "靖儿，把经文默写给他瞧。倘若老毒物真能指得出九阴真经中有一两个错处，老叫化给他磕头。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 7429,
    "line_end": 7429
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "text": "你害了我义兄性命，我跟你仇深似海！你要杀便杀，想要我屈从，那叫做痴心妄想！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 7351,
    "line_end": 7351
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "当今之世，只有你知道真经全文，快写下来罢。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 7349,
    "line_end": 7349
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "臭叫化是一代武学大宗师，总得有些人殉葬，才合他身分。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 7451,
    "line_end": 7451
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "text": "老毒物，今日我就饶了你，上艇罢。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 7495,
    "line_end": 7495
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "老毒物做事向来锲而不舍，不得真经，决不罢休，我这徒儿可要给他缠上了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 7363,
    "line_end": 7363
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "老毒物要九阴真经，你写一部九阴假经与他。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 7415,
    "line_end": 7415
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "你可要写得似是而非，三句真话，夹半句假话，逢到练功的秘诀，却给他增增减减，经上说一的，你给他改成九，说九的改成一。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 7419,
    "line_end": 7419
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我宁可七日七夜不饮酒不吃饭，也要瞧瞧他老毒物练九阴假经的模样。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 7419,
    "line_end": 7419
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "他若照着假经练功，不但虚耗时日，劳而无功，只怕反而身子受害。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 7419,
    "line_end": 7419
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "老叫化武功自成一家，九阴真经就放在面前，也不屑瞧它一眼。只有不成材的厮鸟，自己功夫不成，才巴巴的想偷什么真金真银。",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 7423,
    "line_end": 7423
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "家叔武功已至化境，洪伯父如此本领，却也赢不了家叔一招半式，他又何必再学九阴真经？",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 7427,
    "line_end": 7427
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "臭叫化死到临头，还在梦中喝酒打架。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 7457,
    "line_end": 7457
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_ke",
    "text": "臭叫化是一代武学大宗师，总得有些人殉葬，才合他身分。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 7451,
    "line_end": 7451
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_yang_kang",
    "text": "这大金国的完颜小贼邀了铁掌帮做帮手，暗使奸计害我，偷了帮主的打狗棒来骗人，你们怎么不辨是非，胡乱相信？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 10029,
    "line_end": 10029
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_yang_kang",
    "text": "洪帮主倘若授你打狗棒，怎能不授你打狗棒法？要是授了你打狗棒法，这打狗棒又怎能让我夺来？",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 10031,
    "line_end": 10031
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yang_kang",
    "speaker_name": "杨康",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这是我帮帮主的法杖，什么打狗棒不打狗棒，这么难听！休得胡言，亵渎了宝物。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 10033,
    "line_end": 10033
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "对你也用得着打狗棒法？你配么？",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 10053,
    "line_end": 10053
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "简长老",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "黄姑娘手下容情，我服你啦！",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 10093,
    "line_end": 10093
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你叫我什么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 10095,
    "line_end": 10095
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "简长老",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "对，对！小人该死，小人参见帮主。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 10095,
    "line_end": 10095
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "靖哥哥，你说真经中有什么'移魂大法'？",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 10107,
    "line_end": 10107
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "好啦，你去点了他穴道。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 10123,
    "line_end": 10123
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "现下洪帮主未归，由我暂且署理帮主事宜。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 10131,
    "line_end": 10131
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "洪帮主将打狗棒传给谁了？难道还不明白么？",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 10045,
    "line_end": 10045
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_you_jiao",
    "speaker_name": "鲁有脚",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "众位兄弟，这位姑娘适才出手，当真是老帮主的功夫。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 10047,
    "line_end": 10047
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_qiu_qian_ren",
    "text": "裘老爷子，天地真小，咱俩又见面啦。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 10157,
    "line_end": 10157
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "昨晚咱俩受丐帮阵法挤迫，眼见性命不保，你干么撇开我？难道你死了我还能活么？难道你到今天还不知道我的心么？",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 28,
    "line_start": 10143,
    "line_end": 10143
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "是我不好，咱俩原该死在一起才是。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 28,
    "line_start": 10145,
    "line_end": 10145
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "只要你心中永远待我好，你就是娶了她，我也不在乎。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 28,
    "line_start": 9252,
    "line_end": 9252
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "这份亲事是大汗给我定的。那时候我没有不喜欢，也没觉得很喜欢⋯⋯现今，蓉儿啊，我怎能撇下你去另娶别人？反正我只娶你，如果我不能娶你，我说什么也不能活了。",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 28,
    "line_start": 9250,
    "line_end": 9250
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yang_kang",
    "speaker_name": "杨康",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "她是我未过门的妻子，你屡加戏侮，我岂能容你？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 28,
    "line_start": 9210,
    "line_end": 9210
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我姓欧阳的纵横半生，想不到今日死在你这小子手里。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 28,
    "line_start": 9206,
    "line_end": 9206
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_nian_ci",
    "speaker_name": "穆念慈",
    "listener": "char_yang_kang",
    "text": "你认贼作父，还可说是顾念旧情，一时心里转不过来。那知你竟存非份之想，还要灭了自己的父母之邦。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 28,
    "line_start": 6123,
    "line_end": 6123
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_nian_ci",
    "speaker_name": "穆念慈",
    "listener": "char_yang_kang",
    "text": "你叫他'爹'不挺好么？这可亲热得多，干么要叫'父王'？",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 28,
    "line_start": 6119,
    "line_end": 6119
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yang_kang",
    "speaker_name": "杨康",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "富贵，哼，我又有什么富贵？大金国的中都也给蒙古人攻下了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 28,
    "line_start": 9230,
    "line_end": 9230
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_nian_ci",
    "speaker_name": "穆念慈",
    "listener": "char_yang_kang",
    "text": "你是愿意作大宋的忠义之民呢，还是贪图富贵不可限量，仍要去认贼作父？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 28,
    "line_start": 9228,
    "line_end": 9228
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_yao_shi",
    "speaker_name": "黄药师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "黄老邪生平最恨的是虚伪礼法，最恶的是伪圣假贤，这些都是欺骗愚夫愚妇的东西。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 28,
    "line_start": 9068,
    "line_end": 9068
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_yao_shi",
    "speaker_name": "黄药师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你是桃花岛门人，难道也守世俗的礼法？来来来，两人并排站着，向外拜天！",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 28,
    "line_start": 9088,
    "line_end": 9088
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yi_deng",
    "speaker_name": "一灯大师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我心肠刚硬，不肯救那孩子性命，此后十来年中，日日夜夜教我不得安息，总盼多救世人，赎此大罪。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 11077,
    "line_end": 11077
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yi_deng",
    "speaker_name": "一灯大师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "她向我望了一眼，这是最后的一眼，眼色中充满了怨毒与仇恨。她以后永远没再瞧我，可是这一眼我到死也忘不了。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 11055,
    "line_end": 11055
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yi_deng",
    "speaker_name": "一灯大师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "孩子，妈没本事救你，妈却能教你不再受苦，你安安静静的睡罢，孩子，你永远不会醒啦！",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 11060,
    "line_end": 11060
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yi_deng",
    "speaker_name": "一灯大师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "总有一日，我要用这匕首在你心口也戳一刀。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 11064,
    "line_end": 11064
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_yi_deng",
    "text": "师伯，其实你心中十分爱她，一点儿也没讲错。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 11038,
    "line_end": 11038
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_yi_deng",
    "text": "世间恩仇之际，原也难明。我爹爹在桃花岛上将老顽童周伯通关了一十五年，终也救不活我妈妈的性命。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 11164,
    "line_end": 11164
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ying_gu",
    "speaker_name": "锳姑",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "段智兴，你到底见我不见？在黑暗里缩头藏尾，算是什么大丈夫的行迳？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 11192,
    "line_end": 11192
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ying_gu",
    "speaker_name": "锳姑",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "放开我，我要抱孩子！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 11055,
    "line_end": 11055
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yi_deng",
    "speaker_name": "一灯大师",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "你宅心忠厚，将来必有大成。锳姑的事，我重托你了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 11101,
    "line_end": 11101
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_ying_gu",
    "text": "冤有头，债有主，是谁害死你心爱之人，你该走遍天涯海角，找这真凶报仇才是。迁怒旁人，又有何用？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 11172,
    "line_end": 11172
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_ying_gu",
    "text": "老顽童最肯听我的话，我说什么他从来不会驳回。你若想见他，这就跟我下山。我为你们撮合良缘。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 11178,
    "line_end": 11178
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ying_gu",
    "speaker_name": "锳姑",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "杀了你又怎样？别人忌惮黄老邪，我却天不怕地不怕。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 11180,
    "line_end": 11180
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_ying_gu",
    "text": "杀了我不打紧，谁给你解那三道算题啊？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 11180,
    "line_end": 11180
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "我正要问你，那小丫头在那里？快交出人来！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 12858,
    "line_end": 12858
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "text": "她聪明伶俐，倘若想逃，定然逃得了。她是怎生逃了的？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 12862,
    "line_end": 12862
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "傻小子，咱俩订个约怎样？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 12876,
    "line_end": 12876
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "text": "你要黄姑娘给你解释九阴真经，她肯与不肯，只能由她，你不能伤她毫发。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 12898,
    "line_end": 12898
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "text": "从今而后，你落在我手中之时，我饶你三次不死。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 12898,
    "line_end": 12898
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我欧阳锋竟要你这臭小子相饶？好罢，咱们走着瞧。",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 12902,
    "line_end": 12902
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "丈夫一言。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 12902,
    "line_end": 12902
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "快马一鞭。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 12902,
    "line_end": 12902
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "十日之内，再来相访，且瞧是你饶我，还是我饶你？",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 12904,
    "line_end": 12904
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我常常觉得，黄姑娘就在我身边，我有什么疑难不决之事，她总是给我出个极妙的主意。只不管我怎么想念，却始终见不着她。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 12908,
    "line_end": 12908
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "若不是见你想得我苦，才不来会你呢。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 13036,
    "line_end": 13036
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "蓉儿。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 13036,
    "line_end": 13036
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "你还叫不够么？这些日子来，我虽不在你眼前，难道你每天不是叫我几十遍么？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 13038,
    "line_end": 13038
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "想到你在桃花岛上这般待我，你说我该不该饶你？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 13044,
    "line_end": 13044
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "蓉儿，我给你磕一百个响头赔罪。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 13044,
    "line_end": 13044
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "先前只道你一心一意就想给师父报仇，心里没我这个人半点影子，我自然生气啦！后来见你跟欧阳锋立约，只要他不害我，你可饶他三次不死，倒不急着报仇啦！这么说，你倒当真把我瞧得比为你师父报仇要紧些。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 13046,
    "line_end": 13046
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "你到这时候才知道我的心。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 13046,
    "line_end": 13046
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "靖哥哥，以后你永远别离开我，好不好？",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 13058,
    "line_end": 13058
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_you_jiao",
    "speaker_name": "鲁有脚",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "黄帮主料事如神⋯⋯",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 12926,
    "line_end": 12926
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "我送一份大礼给你，你欢不欢喜？撒麻尔罕城。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 37,
    "line_start": 13110,
    "line_end": 13110
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "text": "老叫化，你今日跟我是比武决胜呢，还是性命相拚？",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13807,
    "line_end": 13807
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "text": "既赌胜负，亦决死生，你下手不必容情。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13807,
    "line_end": 13807
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "华山比武不好，还是到船里去比。好让欧阳先生再来一次恩将仇报、背后袭击啊！",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13809,
    "line_end": 13809
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "欧阳锋啊欧阳锋，有一件事，普天下当真无人及得上你老人家，那就是不要脸天下第一！",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13829,
    "line_end": 13829
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "欧阳兄，老叫化服了你啦，你是武功天下第一！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13935,
    "line_end": 13935
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我九阴真经上的神功已然练成，我的武功天下第一！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13901,
    "line_end": 13901
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我是谁？我在那里？我怎么了？",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13947,
    "line_end": 13947
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "text": "谁说你是天下第一？有一个人你就打不过。他名叫欧阳锋。",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13941,
    "line_end": 13943
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "让你天下第一，我认输便是。别追我，别追我！",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13957,
    "line_end": 13957
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_yao_shi",
    "speaker_name": "黄药师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "七兄，武学之道无穷无尽，今日见识到老毒物的武功，实令人又惊又愧。自重阳真人逝世，从此更无武功天下第一之人了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13967,
    "line_end": 13967
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "蓉儿的烹调功夫天下第一，这个我却敢说。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13969,
    "line_end": 13969
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "不用赞啦，咱们快下山去，我给你烧几样好菜就是。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13971,
    "line_end": 13971
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_yao_shi",
    "speaker_name": "黄药师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "靖儿，你母亡故，世上最亲之人就是你大师父柯镇恶了，你随我回桃花岛去，请你大师父主婚，完了你与蓉儿的婚事如何？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13975,
    "line_end": 13975
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "爹爹真好，放咱俩小夫妻自由自在的胡闹，他眼不见为净。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13977,
    "line_end": 13977
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "咱们既学了武穆遗书中的兵法，又岂能不受岳武穆'尽忠报国'四字之教？他教的虽是'破金'，其实是'破敌'，用以'破蒙'，那也无妨。咱俩虽人微力薄，却也要尽心竭力，为国御侮。纵然捐躯沙场，也不枉了父母师长教养一场。",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 14041,
    "line_end": 14041
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我原知难免有此一日。罢罢罢，你活我也活，你死我也死就是！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 14041,
    "line_end": 14041
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我？我是谁？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13961,
    "line_end": 13961
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "你是郭靖。靖哥哥，快别想自己，多想想人家的事罢。",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13961,
    "line_end": 13961
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "岳父爹爹！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13965,
    "line_end": 13965
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我去也。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 13973,
    "line_end": 13973
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_nian_ci",
    "speaker_name": "穆念慈",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "郭大哥，请你给这孩儿取个名字。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 14005,
    "line_end": 14005
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我给他取个名字叫作杨过，字改之，你说好不好？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 14007,
    "line_end": 14007
  }
]